{
    "info": {
        "name": "VaxTrack — Driver (Eicher & Pickup) Module",
        "_postman_id": "vaxtrack-driver-v1-2026",
        "description": "VaxTrack — Driver module. JWT role must be exactly driver eicher or driver pickup (User model enum). Login captures {{driverToken}}.\n\nE2E: set {{assignmentId}} from OM collection after logistics assign. Trip submit does not complete the enquiry; OM packing approval does.",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
    },
    "variable": [
        {
            "key": "baseUrl",
            "value": "http://localhost:5000",
            "type": "string"
        },
        {
            "key": "driverToken",
            "value": "",
            "type": "string"
        },
        {
            "key": "assignmentId",
            "value": "",
            "type": "string"
        }
    ],
    "item": [
        {
            "name": "0. Auth",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "Login as Driver",
                    "event": [
                        {
                            "listen": "test",
                            "script": {
                                "exec": [
                                    "const res = pm.response.json();",
                                    "if (res.token) {",
                                    "  pm.collectionVariables.set('driverToken', res.token);",
                                    "  console.log('Driver Token captured:', res.token);",
                                    "}"
                                ],
                                "type": "text/javascript"
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n  \"mobileNo\": \"1000000000\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/login",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "users",
                                "login"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Login. Important: The backend auto-detects if this user is an Eicher or Pickup driver from their role."
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "GET My Profile",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{driverToken}}"
                            }
                        ],
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/me",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "users",
                                "me"
                            ]
                        }
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "POST Logout",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{driverToken}}"
                            }
                        ],
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/logout",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "users",
                                "logout"
                            ]
                        }
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "1. Daily Logs",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "GET Check Today Log Status",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{driverToken}}"
                            }
                        ],
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/daily-logs/check-today",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "daily-logs",
                                "check-today"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "🚦 CALL THIS FIRST ON APP OPEN.\n\nChecks if the logged-in Driver has already submitted a Start Day log for today.\n\n- `isStarted: true`  → skip the meter photo screen, jump to dashboard. Use the returned `logId` for any log-specific operations.\n- `isStarted: false` → show the Start Day / Meter Photo screen.\n\nResponse:\n```json\n// Day already started:\n{ \"isStarted\": true, \"logId\": \"<ObjectId>\", \"role\": \"driver eicher\" }\n\n// Day not started:\n{ \"isStarted\": false }\n```"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "POST Start Day Log",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{driverToken}}"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "formdata",
                            "formdata": [
                                {
                                    "key": "startKm",
                                    "value": "46820",
                                    "type": "text"
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "vehicleNumber",
                                    "value": "MH-15-E2E-4404",
                                    "type": "text"
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "petrolAdvance",
                                    "value": "0",
                                    "type": "text"
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "startKmPhoto",
                                    "type": "file",
                                    "src": ""
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "petrolReceiptPhoto",
                                    "type": "file",
                                    "src": "",
                                    "description": "Optional"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/daily-logs/start",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "daily-logs",
                                "start"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Call this when the driver starts their day. Upload odometer photo."
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "PATCH End Day Log",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "PATCH",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{driverToken}}"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "formdata",
                            "formdata": [
                                {
                                    "key": "endKm",
                                    "value": "46990",
                                    "type": "text"
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "endKmPhoto",
                                    "type": "file",
                                    "src": ""
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/daily-logs/end",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "daily-logs",
                                "end"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Call this to end the active day log."
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "2. Dashboard",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "GET Driver Dashboard (Active Trips)",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{driverToken}}"
                            }
                        ],
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/driver/dashboard",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "driver",
                                "dashboard"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Fetches active assignments where this driver is either the primary driverId (Eicher) or pickupDriverId (Pickup)."
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "3. Submit Trip Report",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "A. Submit Trip Report (Eicher Example)",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{driverToken}}"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "formdata",
                            "formdata": [
                                {
                                    "key": "totalKm",
                                    "value": "150",
                                    "type": "text"
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "tollExpense",
                                    "value": "200",
                                    "type": "text"
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "isHault",
                                    "value": "false",
                                    "type": "text"
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "isLineCancel",
                                    "value": "false",
                                    "type": "text"
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "startRoute",
                                    "value": "Farm A",
                                    "type": "text"
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "midRoute",
                                    "value": "Highway Cafe",
                                    "type": "text"
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "destination",
                                    "value": "Cold Storage",
                                    "type": "text"
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "weightSlipPhoto",
                                    "type": "file",
                                    "src": ""
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "dieselSlipPhoto",
                                    "type": "file",
                                    "src": ""
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "unloadSlipPhoto",
                                    "type": "file",
                                    "src": ""
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/driver/trips/{{assignmentId}}",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "driver",
                                "trips",
                                "{{assignmentId}}"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Submits a standard Eicher trip report with flat route fields and 3 specific file uploads.\n\n**State:** Creates Trip only. Does **not** set parent Enquiry to COMPLETED (OM packing approval closes the enquiry)."
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "B. Submit Trip Report (Pickup Example)",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{driverToken}}"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "formdata",
                            "formdata": [
                                {
                                    "key": "totalKm",
                                    "value": "45",
                                    "type": "text"
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "tollExpense",
                                    "value": "0",
                                    "type": "text"
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "routes",
                                    "value": "[{\"startPoint\":\"Base\",\"destination\":\"Farm A\",\"task\":\"Pickup Crates\"},{\"startPoint\":\"Farm A\",\"destination\":\"Weighbridge\",\"task\":\"Weighing\"}]",
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "description": "Send array as JSON string if using form-data"
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "uploadSlipPhoto",
                                    "type": "file",
                                    "src": ""
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "meterPhoto",
                                    "type": "file",
                                    "src": ""
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/driver/trips/{{assignmentId}}",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "driver",
                                "trips",
                                "{{assignmentId}}"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Submits a Pickup driver report using the multi-route array (sent as a JSON string in form-data) and 2 specific file uploads.\n\n**State:** Creates Trip only; does **not** complete the parent Enquiry."
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "4. History & Reports",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "GET Paginated History",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{driverToken}}"
                            }
                        ],
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/driver/history?page=1&limit=20",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "driver",
                                "history"
                            ],
                            "query": [
                                {
                                    "key": "page",
                                    "value": "1"
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "limit",
                                    "value": "20"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Returns completed trips scoped to this driver."
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "GET Monthly Report & Earnings",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{driverToken}}"
                            }
                        ],
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/driver/reports?month=3&year=2026",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "driver",
                                "reports"
                            ],
                            "query": [
                                {
                                    "key": "month",
                                    "value": "3"
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "year",
                                    "value": "2026"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Returns monthly totals (KM, tolls, trips, haults, fuel advances) and a daily trip log grouped by date."
                    }
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}
